OL,9,FDavid Beckham and Gary Neville are
OL,10,Fpart of a new ownership group at
OL,11,FLeague Two club Salford City.
OL,13,FThe club announced the former
OL,14,FManchester United stars were part of a
OL,15,Fconsortium which also includes a US-
OL,16,Fbased businessman, Declan Kelly, and
OL,17,FLord Mervyn Davies.
