OL,3,CDavid Beckham and Gary Neville part of
OL,4,Cnew ownership group at Salford
OL,6,FBeckham first invested in Salford in
OL,7,FJanuary 2019, joining former 'Class of
OL,8,F92' team-mates Neville, Phil Neville,
OL,9,FPaul Scholes, Ryan Giggs and Nicky
OL,10,FButt as a shareholder.
OL,12,FGary Neville bought out the stake of
OL,13,Fformer co-owner Peter Lim last August.
OL,14,FThe club confirmed on Thursday that
OL,15,FPhil Neville, Scholes, Giggs and Butt
OL,16,Fwere no longer shareholders but would
OL,17,Fstill be contributing to the club
OL,18,F"with roles in the club across
OL,19,Ftechnical, football, commercial,
OL,20,Frecruitment and the SCFC foundation".
