OL,6,FKelly and Davies will serve as co-
OL,7,Fchairs on the club's board.
OL,9,FThe club said the acquisition includes
OL,10,F"a commitment by the new shareholders
OL,11,Fto invest significantly in the club,
OL,12,Fthe team and its facilities".
OL,14,FSalford missed out on the League Two
OL,15,Fplay-offs by a single point, so will
OL,16,Fagain play in English football's
OL,17,Ffourth tier next season.
